WEBVTT

00:00.250 --> 00:01.956
<i>It was a drunken moment of weakness.</i>

00:02.001 --> 00:04.540
<i>It doesn't have to mean
anything more than that.</i>

00:04.713 --> 00:07.922
You need to stay away from Leah.
She's got nothing to do with any of this.

00:08.007 --> 00:10.000
- You're pregnant?
- Yeah.

00:11.470 --> 00:14.383
I've lost my engagement ring.
I think Rose took it.

00:14.431 --> 00:16.158
You sure you don't want
any more wine, Leah?

00:16.183 --> 00:17.264
- Give me that!
- Argh!

00:17.684 --> 00:19.801
<i>She set me up, Adam. She's clever.</i>

00:20.062 --> 00:23.226
Rose isn't just your student.
She's your sister.

00:24.107 --> 00:25.518
Your mother was the coward.

00:25.567 --> 00:29.151
And it's not Pam's fault your mother
didn't love you enough to stick around!

00:29.196 --> 00:31.529
You can't just cheat, Adam,
and expect to get away with it.

00:33.492 --> 00:35.654
St Helen's College, Porter's Office.
How can I help?

00:35.702 --> 00:37.864
Something bad's happened
and I need your help.

00:37.913 --> 00:42.248
You are still not convinced
that we got the right one.

